A cyberpunk-style interior scene of a custom PC being assembled on a cluttered workbench, with exposed motherboard glowing with neon blue and purple circuit traces, multiple graphics cards stacked nearby emanating soft orange light, RAM sticks arranged like futuristic ammunition, all surrounded by holographic displays showing system specs floating in mid-air. The background reveals a rain-streaked window overlooking a dense Asian cityscape with towering LED-covered buildings. Scattered gaming controllers and tangled cables create organized chaos on the desk surface. The overall atmosphere is moody with dramatic rim lighting, combining the intimate craft of building hardware with a futuristic technological aesthetic. Steam or vapor wisps rise from cooling components, adding atmosphere to the scene.
